collectionMetadata.name: Salary Claims by Claim Items
collectionMetadata.description: This dataset includes all salary claims lodged at the Tripartite Alliance for Dispute Management (TADM). Data does not indicate the total number of claims lodged at TADM as one claim may have multiple claim items.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of Salary Claims by Claim Items, Annual
datasetMetadata.description: This dataset includes all salary claims lodged at the Tripartite Alliance for Dispute Management (TADM). A claim can have multiple claim items.
